title: hasbro.interactive.1997.frogger
description:
Frogger returns this time in 3D! Cross endless streets with cars and trucks coming from everywhere. He&#039;s armed with all new moves, a power croak, a heat-seeking tongue, and a super jump! The only difference is he is lost in a dfferent world filled with hungry enemies such as crocodiles, lawnmowers, turtles, and snakes.
ESRB Rating: E for Animated Violence
Genre: Platformer

A great nostalgic game for anybody who&#039;s played Frogger 3D by Hasbro Interactive back in the day, with "Ground Breaking" 3-d graphics and a huge range of fun stages!

This is a complete ISO rip of the original game CD. There is no crack (especially since most of the game info is read from the disc during play) so I would recommend you burn this onto a CD to play it.
